I enjoyed the game up until the point where I figured out how to easily build your tower to epic proportions in a small amount of time. For anyone interested: 
Step 1: open tiny towers and start making goods. 
Step 2: exit the game and open the settings app and change the phones time to manual and move it ahead by the required time. 
Step 3: Open the tiny towers again and stock the store
Step 4: repeat &#34;Step 2&#34;
Step 5: repeat &#34;Step 1 and 2&#34;
Step 6: repeat &#34;Step 3&#34;

Continue until you can afford to build a level. Repeat &#34;Step 2&#34; for all items that take time to finish. 

Before you know it you&#39;ll have your own tiny empire state building!

Good luck :)

Why would you guys need to make a appointment for Genius Bar support when the Geniuses no longer interact with customers, but do the repairs and fixes that are beyond &#34;easy&#34; fixes. 
The store staff is now trained with and tasked to correct all the normal problems. No appointment necessary! If they can&#39;t help they refer you to the geniuses. 
Reminds me of a quote from Blazing Saddles...&#34;they&#39;re people of the land, simple townsfolk...you know, morons.&#34;
